  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690190/extras/8a98c09e40df8f63bfcc48ff34269d22.avif?t=1745420728\" width=500 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an adventure between worlds in the incredible pixel platformer Portal Walk and help Eugene find his way home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for keys, collect fragments of the portal, fight with a lot of difficult enemies and go to other worlds, moving through the levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690190/extras/92187cc5f1abbbaaef56deaeeaf6ec91.poster.avif?t=1745420728\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690190/extras/92187cc5f1abbbaaef56deaeeaf6ec91.webm?t=1745420728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690190/extras/92187cc5f1abbbaaef56deaeeaf6ec91.mp4?t=1745420728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Hardcore Levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Unique Worlds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Action Events</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Challenging Bosses</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Atmospheric Music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Steam Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Support Game Controllers (Playstation DualShock, Xbox Wireless and other)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Indie Cup S'21 – Best Mobile Game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Games Gathering 2021 – Best Art</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valencia Indie Summit 2022 – Selection of Jury</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pocket Gamer 2017 – 7/10, Bronze Award</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Touch Arcade 2017 – Top 3 Hot Games</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690190/extras/8a98c09e40df8f63bfcc48ff34269d22.avif?t=1745420728\" width=500 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an adventure between worlds in the incredible pixel platformer Portal Walk and help Eugene find his way home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for keys, collect fragments of the portal, fight with a lot of difficult enemies and go to other worlds, moving through the levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690190/extras/92187cc5f1abbbaaef56deaeeaf6ec91.poster.avif?t=1745420728\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690190/extras/92187cc5f1abbbaaef56deaeeaf6ec91.webm?t=1745420728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690190/extras/92187cc5f1abbbaaef56deaeeaf6ec91.mp4?t=1745420728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Hardcore Levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Unique Worlds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Action Events</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Challenging Bosses</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Atmospheric Music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Steam Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ● Support Game Controllers (Playstation DualShock, Xbox Wireless and other)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Indie Cup S'21 – Best Mobile Game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Games Gathering 2021 – Best Art</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valencia Indie Summit 2022 – Selection of Jury</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pocket Gamer 2017 – 7/10, Bronze Award</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Touch Arcade 2017 – Top 3 Hot Games</p>",
